{
  "$schema": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/JanDeDobbeleer/oh-my-posh/main/themes/schema.json",
  "version": 4,
  "final_space": true,

  "//": [
    "MiOS Oh-My-Posh theme. Two-line prompt + right-aligned dev language",
    "rollup; recolored to mios.toml [colors] (Hokusai + operator neutrals).",
    "Applied globally on every shape: Windows host (PowerShell via",
    "Install-WindowsBranding), deployed Linux MiOS hosts (via",
    "/etc/profile.d/mios-prompt.sh), and the MiOS-DEV podman backend.",
    "",
    "MiOS-owned segments (shell/path/git/exec/status/os/time) use the MiOS",
    "palette so every prompt FEELS like the same product:",
    "  --bg #282262 deep-indigo  --fg #E7DFD3 cream  --accent #1A407F op-blue",
    "  --cursor/warning #F35C15 sunset  --error #DC271B coral",
    "  --success #3E7765 wave-green  --muted #948E8E warm-grey",
    "  --earth #734F39 brown  --silver #E0E0E0  --subtle #B7C9D7",
    "",
    "Language-version segments (right-aligned) keep their brand colors so",
    "Node green / Python blue+yellow / Rust orange etc. stay instantly",
    "recognizable -- the brand glyph + brand palette is operator memory.",
    "",
    "Every Nerd Font PUA glyph is an explicit UTF-8 codepoint so the file",
    "roundtrips through editor/git/OneDrive sync without losing the",
    "U+E000..U+F8FF code points. Symbols-Only Nerd Font (installed by",
    "automation/09-fonts.sh) is the per-glyph fallback for Geist Mono."
  ],

  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "prompt",
      "alignment": "left",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "shell",
          "style": "diamond",
          "leading_diamond": "╭─",
          "background": "#1A407F",
          "foreground": "#E7DFD3",
          "template": " {{ .Name }} "
        },
        {
          "type": "root",
          "style": "diamond",
          "background": "#DC271B",
          "foreground": "#F35C15",
          "template": "<parentBackground></> # "
        },
        {
          "type": "path",
          "style": "powerline",
          "powerline_symbol": "",
          "background": "#F35C15",
          "foreground": "#282262",
          "properties": {
            "folder_icon": " ",
            "home_icon": "",
            "style": "agnoster_short",
            "max_depth": 3
          },
          "template": "  {{ .Path }} "
        },
        {
          "type": "git",
          "style": "powerline",
          "powerline_symbol": "",
          "background": "#3E7765",
          "background_templates": [
            "{{ if or (.Working.Changed) (.Staging.Changed) }}#F35C15{{ end }}",
            "{{ if and (gt .Ahead 0) (gt .Behind 0) }}#DC271B{{ end }}",
            "{{ if gt .Ahead 0 }}#1A407F{{ end }}",
            "{{ if gt .Behind 0 }}#734F39{{ end }}"
          ],
          "foreground": "#282262",
          "properties": {
            "branch_icon": " ",
            "fetch_status": true,
            "fetch_upstream_icon": true
          },
          "template": " {{ .UpstreamIcon }}{{ .HEAD }}{{ if .BranchStatus }} {{ .BranchStatus }}{{ end }}{{ if .Working.Changed }}  {{ .Working.String }}{{ end }}{{ if and (.Working.Changed) (.Staging.Changed) }} |{{ end }}{{ if .Staging.Changed }}<#DC271B>  {{ .Staging.String }}</>{{ end }} "
        },
        {
          "type": "executiontime",
          "style": "diamond",
          "trailing_diamond": "",
          "background": "#948E8E",
          "foreground": "#282262",
          "properties": {
            "style": "roundrock",
            "threshold": 0
          },
          "template": "  {{ .FormattedMs }} "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "prompt",
      "alignment": "right",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "node",
          "style": "diamond",
          "leading_diamond": "",
          "trailing_diamond": " ",
          "background": "#303030",
          "foreground": "#3C873A",
          "properties": {
            "fetch_package_manager": true,
            "npm_icon": " <#cc3a3a></> ",
            "yarn_icon": " <#348cba></>"
          },
          "template": " {{ if .PackageManagerIcon }}{{ .PackageManagerIcon }} {{ end }}{{ .Full }}"
        },
        {
          "type": "python",
          "style": "diamond",
          "leading_diamond": "",
          "trailing_diamond": " ",
          "background": "#306998",
          "foreground": "#FFE873",
          "template": " {{ if .Error }}{{ .Error }}{{ else }}{{ if .Venv }}{{ .Venv }} {{ end }}{{ .Full }}{{ end }}"
        },
        {
          "type": "go",
          "style": "diamond",
          "leading_diamond": "",
          "trailing_diamond": " ",
          "background": "#E7DFD3",
          "foreground": "#06aad5",
          "template": " {{ if .Error }}{{ .Error }}{{ else }}{{ .Full }}{{ end }}"
        },
        {
          "type": "rust",
          "style": "diamond",
          "leading_diamond": "",
          "trailing_diamond": " ",
          "background": "#E7DFD3",
          "foreground": "#925837",
          "template": " {{ if .Error }}{{ .Error }}{{ else }}{{ .Full }}{{ end }}"
        },
        {
          "type": "dotnet",
          "style": "diamond",
          "leading_diamond": "",
          "trailing_diamond": " ",
          "background": "#0e0e0e",
          "foreground": "#0d6da8",
          "template": " {{ if .Unsupported }}{{ else }}{{ .Full }}{{ end }}"
        },
        {
          "type": "kubectl",
          "style": "diamond",
          "leading_diamond": "",
          "trailing_diamond": " ",
          "background": "#1A407F",
          "foreground": "#E7DFD3",
          "template": " {{ .Context }}{{ if .Namespace }} :: {{ .Namespace }}{{ end }}"
        },
        {
          "type": "aws",
          "style": "diamond",
          "leading_diamond": "",
          "trailing_diamond": " ",
          "background": "#565656",
          "foreground": "#F35C15",
          "template": " {{ .Profile }}{{ if .Region }}@{{ .Region }}{{ end }}"
        },
        {
          "type": "os",
          "style": "diamond",
          "leading_diamond": "",
          "trailing_diamond": "<transparent,background></>",
          "background": "#B7C9D7",
          "foreground": "#282262",
          "properties": {
            "linux": "",
            "macos": "",
            "windows": ""
          },
          "template": " {{ if .WSL }}WSL at {{ end }}{{ .Icon }} "
        },
        {
          "type": "battery",
          "style": "powerline",
          "invert_powerline": true,
          "powerline_symbol": "",
          "background": "#F35C15",
          "background_templates": [
            "{{ if eq \"Charging\" .State.String }}#3E7765{{ end }}",
            "{{ if eq \"Discharging\" .State.String }}#F35C15{{ end }}",
            "{{ if eq \"Full\" .State.String }}#3E7765{{ end }}"
          ],
          "foreground": "#282262",
          "properties": {
            "charged_icon": " ",
            "charging_icon": " ",
            "discharging_icon": " "
          },
          "template": " {{ if not .Error }}{{ .Icon }}{{ .Percentage }}{{ end }}{{ .Error }} "
        },
        {
          "type": "time",
          "style": "diamond",
          "invert_powerline": true,
          "leading_diamond": "",
          "trailing_diamond": "",
          "background": "#1A407F",
          "foreground": "#E7DFD3",
          "properties": {
            "time_format": "_2,15:04"
          },
          "template": "  {{ .CurrentDate | date .Format }} "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "prompt",
      "alignment": "left",
      "newline": true,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "style": "plain",
          "foreground": "#B7C9D7",
          "template": "╰─"
        },
        {
          "type": "status",
          "style": "plain",
          "foreground": "#3E7765",
          "foreground_templates": [
            "{{ if gt .Code 0 }}#DC271B{{ end }}"
          ],
          "properties": { "always_enabled": true },
          "template": " ❯ "
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
